    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Quikr International Enterprises. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Software Engineer to strengthen our Patna-based team.\n\nAbout Quikr International Enterprises:\nQuikr International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Quikr International Enterprises!",
